Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:01:59.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.68,0:02:04.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.04,0:02:06.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:07.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:07.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.27,0:02:09.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:22.87,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:26.95,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:30.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 我犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:32.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:35.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.80,0:02:38.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.24,0:02:41.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,要快点去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:45.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,去苍乃那里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.69,0:02:57.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 伤口不会自己愈合了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说 夜祸的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.12,0:03:06.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到会让你来背我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:06.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要我背吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.70,0:03:08.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:12.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是在想也许不会再有这种事了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.18,0:03:17.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是今天这样的天空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.63,0:03:20.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,和依人相遇的那时候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:21.47,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是卷积云
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:26.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然还记得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是依人教我的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:33.00,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,断层云 积雨云
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:37.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,卷云 层云 积云 还有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:37.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.99,0:03:41.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,结果还是没有让你看到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:42.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.03,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不 你已经让我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:47.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:52.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看过的天空 你追逐的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:55.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,透过你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:03.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:09.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜祸的力量正在变弱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:19.12,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:24.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 你留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:27.66,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来我一个人不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:29.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:32.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不想再让你看下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我和苍乃战斗时的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.90,0:04:37.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.05,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要担心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还能相见的 一定还能相见的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.14,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,别说那种一眼就看穿的谎话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:24.72,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我也没其他地方好去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:29.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实是必须要把性命献给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为村子里有恶灵作祟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.98,0:05:34.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:37.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:43.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你不可能做那样的事 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:45.15,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来到这里 总觉得明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:50.24,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会让别人不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:52.80,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个人在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:00.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:02.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.76,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃的时候要笑出来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:09.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,笑？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:14.19,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.57,0:06:26.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起你的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.65,0:06:28.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:32.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.20,0:06:38.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是你教会了我什么是心 人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以会痛苦 悲伤 难过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.46,0:06:43.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.63,0:06:46.71,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,但是总比不知道的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:48.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说漂亮的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:48.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真的这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:56.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要把你变回去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.02,0:06:59.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把必须接受依人死的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会如你所愿的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:21.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:24.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就可以看到天空了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:04.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:16.43,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.60,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.61,0:08:21.18,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.52,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:29.32,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:31.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:46.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 不要 不要 不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.29,0:08:49.46,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人 依人 依人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:53.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 我不会再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:57.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就能把一切恢复原样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人 依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:10.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我把我的生命给你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.42,0:09:30.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:31.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:38.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,依人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,如果可以的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:56.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我最后许一次愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:10:01.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,三个人一起看到的 那时的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:05.54,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,无法到达的 遥远的约定的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:09.84,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:10.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.04,0:10:12.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,别问啦 别问啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来这里躺下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:25.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:29.33,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来打算画个天空的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点勉强吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.44,0:10:36.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空 这就是天空
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:38.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.90,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,茉莉总有一天会看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.72,0:11:33.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:35.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怪物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:37.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真没礼貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.31,0:11:51.27,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:52.75,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,他在哭哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:58.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是他自己偷看 又自己逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.28,0:12:03.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我一直想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:16.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你衣服的品味一年比一年差了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.08,0:12:21.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,脑袋差点被扭下来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:22.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.18,0:12:30.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 刚史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.92,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚史为什么没有逃走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:35.59,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.24,0:12:39.53,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.15,0:12:43.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没理由逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:47.62,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,刚史
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:52.82,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 趁雨还没停我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 刚史
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:52.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又是折纸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.85,0:13:54.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你还真是折不腻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:57.77,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 折纸其实很复杂的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:00.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把这里折起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.15,0:14:02.08,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,折好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:08.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:12.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您亲切的问候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.16,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名一直以来受你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:18.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.42,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.63,0:14:22.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.89,0:14:24.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,小依太可怜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.90,0:14:27.51,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就是啊 明明那么可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.18,0:14:31.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是一个粗野的姐姐啊 委屈你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.32,0:14:37.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,都高二了 都说让你也稍微学着沉着一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.69,0:14:39.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.94,0:14:43.49,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 为什么我要被你们训话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.61,0:14:49.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请问要点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:55.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,今天推荐的是章鱼和罗勒做的意大利冷面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.31,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一点都不像是在推荐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:00.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,点了的话好像要吃坏肚子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 你也该打起精神来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.88,0:15:05.09,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,事情都过了一年了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.22,0:15:12.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.93,0:15:17.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得绝对不会再有比胡子绅士更好的男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,玩弄了我纯洁的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.63,0:15:21.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,连招呼都不打一声
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,就消失得无影无踪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.21,0:15:24.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,太过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.94,0:15:26.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,已经听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:28.58,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真名 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:33.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,话说真名怎么不回来打工呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.37,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,她一个人是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:36.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不干了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:40.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.13,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.79,0:15:46.25,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想改变一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:47.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,改变什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.99,0:15:49.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.48,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,比起钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:13.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想再长高点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.04,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:25.74,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:38.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,折好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.11,0:16:45.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 可不可以拿着这只船的另一头
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:47.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,然后闭上眼睛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.27,0:16:48.94,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.03,0:16:55.86,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 请睁开眼睛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:02.97,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你已经知道了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:05.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,给真名看的时候明明…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.13,0:17:13.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还能再多教我一点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:14.73,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:52.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是非常感谢你 能够陪我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:54.50,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,那么再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.57,0:17:56.07,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:01.36,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,可以告诉我你的名字吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.30,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.85,0:18:06.17,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,森宫苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:09.67,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:35.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,数学作业已经交了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.64,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.35,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,请问
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:18.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,你是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.66,0:19:19.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,凉嗖嗖地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:22.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,这个太短了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.26,0:19:27.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你是转校生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.10,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.64,0:19:29.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:32.85,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,在看天空吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.21,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.86,0:19:37.91,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里看到的天空很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.78,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,特别是晚霞很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:44.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我每天放学后都要到这里来看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:46.83,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.40,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢 大概在以前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:57.38,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我自己也不清楚 可就是觉得喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.56,0:20:01.11,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常喜欢天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.98,0:20:07.70,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:12.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这宽广的天空把一切都连接起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:17.06,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,把人 海 城市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.34,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还有夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.78,0:20:21.44,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:22.61,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.20,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,天空的另一面就是夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:29.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,一个同样连接在一起的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.07,0:20:31.96,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:36.26,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我会走在天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:39.63,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,走在那两个人送给我的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:51.39,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 天空 喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.68,0:20:55.01,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:05.68,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:23.81,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好困
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:33.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐再不起来 太阳就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.02,0:21:38.98,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 快点起来 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.78,0:21:50.56,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,不错的早晨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.49,0:21:52.89,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.08,0:21:54.29,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,是 真名
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.03,0:22:26.69,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:35.45,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.50,0:22:40.88,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好像小依非常喜欢苍乃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.67,0:22:43.28,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.23,0:22:58.79,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还没好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:00.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.16,0:23:10.23,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪 明明把钱投进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:11.57,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,让一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.21,0:23:19.65,Default1,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:43.04,FBT,NTP,0,0,360,,{\fad(500,500)}sola
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何気ない言葉さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}刻まれた胸が熱い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:30.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}当たり前のように　過ごした日々が遠いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:35.59,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}かけがえのない人が
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:40.67,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}幸せに照らされて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:48.69,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}悲しみさえ霞んでく幻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:54.02,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}やがて消えた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.85,0:21:59.23,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Remember on my mind, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:05.41,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}流れるあの雲に　心重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:13.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}今を青く漂えば　愛しい君へと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:20.91,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いだけが　Ah...　伝わればいいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:29.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}誰も知らない未来　いつか会いたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:39.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}その時を待ってる　見上げるあの空で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:56.32,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}想いだけが　Ah...　伝わればいいんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:04.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}何もいらない　ただねひとつの夢をね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:15.30,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}感じてたと思うよ　見上げるあの空で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.16,0:21:17.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不经意的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在我心中荡漾不已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.51,0:21:30.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}过去的日子　也理所当然地远去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:35.59,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}那无可取代的人儿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.53,0:21:40.67,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}正沐浴在幸福的阳光下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:48.69,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}就连悲伤　和那朦胧的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.08,0:21:54.02,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}也终于消逝在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.46,0:22:05.41,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我们心心相映　在那流动的云彩里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.46,0:22:13.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}倘若身驾祥云　一定要去往心爱的你那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.60,0:22:20.91,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕只是一份心意　啊…　真想传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:29.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}让我们相遇　在那未知的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:39.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}我等待在　这苍穹之下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.91,0:22:56.32,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}哪怕只是一份心意　啊…　真想传递给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.55,0:23:04.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}什么都不需要了　这不过是一场梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.77,0:23:15.30,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}但我已经体味过了　在这苍穹之下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:22.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}羽根が白く光り 眩しく飛んで行く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:28.86,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}心だけ乗せて欲しいのに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:36.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たい手を伸ばす 届かない…知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:44.11,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}だけどいま触れたい君に
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:50.53,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}懐かしい風には あの頃の舟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:59.19,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}幻が思い出を見せた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:08.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れない」誰かの声が切なく響く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:14.06,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}始まる予感にふるえて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:22.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「忘れたい」願う自分がわからない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:33.91,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}待っている 揺られながら夢ひとつを
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.89,0:00:22.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}雪白闪亮的羽毛飞向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.61,0:00:28.86,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}它要是能带上我的心意多好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.34,0:00:36.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}伸出冰冷的双手 明明知道触摸不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:44.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}可是现在想碰触到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:50.53,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}令人怀念的微风像那时候的小船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:59.19,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}呈现出梦幻的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:08.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「不要忘记」耳边想起悲伤的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:14.06,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}害怕那要发生什么的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:22.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}「想要忘记」却不知自己为何如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:33.91,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,2000)}带着一个梦想和心中的动摇 等着你
